description:
This is a 33 minute workout called 'PCOS Home Workout for Weight Loss + Belly Fat' from the channel PCOS Weight Loss.
The workout falls under Strength/Weight workout and Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Weights and Other for this workout.
The workout has a The Progression Quest and The Foundation Builder vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate.
